quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  25,21,"Iwo amene alibe chikhulupiriro choti adzakumana ndi Ife amati, “Kodi ndi chifukwa chiyani angelo sadatumizidwe kwa ife? Kapena ndi chifukwa chiyani kuti ife sitingaone Ambuye wathu?” Ndithudi iwo adadzikweza kwambiri"
  25,22,"Patsiku limene iwo adzaona angelo, anthu ochita zoipa sadzasangalala ayi ndipo iwo adzati, “Ambuye wathu! Ikani malire pakati pa ife ndi iwo.”"
  25,23,Ndipo Ife tidzabweretsa zonse zimene adachita ndikuzionetsa kuti ndi zinthu zopanda ntchito ngati fumbi louluka
  25,24,"Anthu okhala ku Paradiso, adzakhala kumalo abwino patsiku limeneli ndiponso malo abwino opumulako"
  25,25,Patsiku limeneli kumwamba pamodzi ndi mitambo yake idzagawanika pakati ndipo angelo adzatumizidwa pansi pano m’maudindo awo
  25,26,Patsiku limeneli ufumu wonse udzakhala wa Mwini chisoni chosatha. Limeneli lidzakhala tsiku lovuta kwambiri kwa anthu osakhulupirira
  25,27,"Patsiku limeneli munthu ochita zoipa adzanong’oneza bombono nati, “Oh zikadakhala bwino ndikadakhala kuti ndidatsatira zimene Mtumwi anali kunena!”"
  25,28,“oh kalanga ine! Ndikadakhala kuti sindidasankhe a uje ndi a uje kuti akhale anzanga!”
  25,29,“Mosakayika ndiwo amene adandisokoneza ine kuti ndisakhulupirire machenjezo a Mulungu pamene machenjezowo atandifika. Ndithudi Satana ndi wachinyengo nthawi zonse kwa munthu.”
  25,30,"Mtumwi adati, “Ambuye wanga! Ndithudi anthu anga alikana Buku la Korani.”"
  25,31,"Motero Ife tapanga kwa Mtumwi aliyense mdani kuchokera kwa anthu ochimwa, anthu otsutsana naye, ndipo Ambuye wako ali wokwana kukhala wokutsogolera mu zabwino ndiponso ngati wokuthandiza wako"
  25,32,"Anthu osakhulupirira anati, “Kodi ndi chifukwa chiyani Korani yonse siidavumbulutsidwe kwa iye nthawi imodzi?” Ife talivumbulutsa kotero kuti tikhoza kulimbikitsa mtima wako ndipo takupatsa ilo kwa iwe mu chivumbulutso chapang’onopang’ono"